    "The results suggest that the hybrid CNN-RNN model significantly outperformed the other three models to varying extent.",
    "The weak performance of LASSO was mainly due to its linear property, which could not capture the nonlinear effects of soil conditions and weather components.",
    "The DFNN performed better than LASSO since DFNN was able to capture the nonlinear effects of environmental components.",
    "DFNN had a better performance compared to the RF model with respect to all performance measures except the validation RMSE of the year for corn yield prediction.",
